highlights.text: “Hva' Chancen” by Kundo and Thor Farlov is the highest new entry on Top Songs Denmark at #10.
“Reposado” by Benny Jamz and Gilli has been on Top Songs Denmark the longest, at 449 days straight.
Lamin has the most spots on Top Songs Denmark. “Stolt (feat. Lamin)” is the highest at #6.
“A Little More” by Ed Sheeran is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Denmark, up 84 spots at #70.
